ARGUMENT
y

| Step | Hyp | Ref | Expression |
|---|---|---|---|

| 1 |  | #P_nfv | |- F/ y ph |
| 2 | 1 | #P_eu1 | |- ( E! x ph <-> E. x ( ph /\ A. y ( [ y / x ] ph -> x = y ) ) ) |
| 3 |  | #P_exsimpl | |- ( E. x ( ph /\ A. y ( [ y / x ] ph -> x = y ) ) -> E. x ph ) |
| 4 | 2, 3 | #P_sylbi | |- ( E! x ph -> E. x ph ) |
\
 Alternate proof of ~ euex .  Shorter but uses more axioms.  (Contributed by NM, 15-Sep-1993.)  (Proof shortened by Andrew Salmon, 9-Jul-2011.) (Proof modification is discouraged.)  (New usage is discouraged.)
